大概平時返工四成左右, <br />\n<br />\n諗落都覺得好笑, 我辛苦工作, 為左就係六七十歲後, 可以享受類似咁既休閒寧靜既生活 <br />\n<br />\n原來失業已經可以做到, 人生真係可笑, 哈哈"},{"pid":"ef701699b3393691a82aa6714cc75beb2f2205d8","tid":466343,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:36:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日一返工就頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚份part time先係自己鐘意但齋做part time生活唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最好乜都唔駛做"}]}